df['dc_asthma'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'asthma' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_atherosclerosis'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'atherosclerosis' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_azotemia'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'azotemia' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_bronchitis'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'bronchitis' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_cancer'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'cancer' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_diabetes'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'diabetes' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_hepatitis'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'hepatitis' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_hypertensive'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'hypertensi' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_hyperthyroidism'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'hyperthyroidism' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_kidney'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'kidney' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_parkinson'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'Parkinson' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_prostatic'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'prostat' in str(x) else 0 )
df['dc_renal'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'renal' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_tuberculosis'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'uberculosis' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_dyslipidemia'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if 'dyslipidemia' in str(x) else 0)
df['dc_cerebral'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if ( ('cerebral infarction' in str(x)) or ('cerebrovascular' in str(x)) )  else 0 )
df['dc_copd'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if (('COPD' in str(x)) or ('obstructive pulmonary' in str(x)))  else 0 )
df['dc_cardiac'] = df['chronic_disease'].apply(lambda x: 1 if ( ('cardiac' in str(x)) or ('heart' in str(x)) or ('coronary' in str(x)) )  else 0 )

df = df.drop(columns='chronic_disease')
